Connamon, Potato and Onion Soup for 1

An improv recipe by Jonathan. Slightly hot, nice'n'thick.

1 Clove Garlic
1 Large Onion, Chopped
3 Medium Potatos, Cubed
500ml Stock
1tsb Basil
1/2tsb Black Pepper
1/2tsp Cinnamon

Blend(
	Simmer 20 min(
		Stock,
		fry 1 min(
			fry til soft (Large Onion, Garlic),
			Medium Potatos
		)
	),
	Basil,
	Black Pepper,
	Cinnamon
)
